title: GDG DevFest 2018
subtitle: San Francisco • Fremont
blurbContent: A one day community-run event designed to facilitate the exchange of ideas between developers of all skill levels and backgrounds. Participants will gain access to all speaker sessions.
submitContent: Interested in giving a talk? Submit a proposal to become one of our speakers. Each sessions will 45 minutes long, with a 15 minute break in between.
